{"tid":1351002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文：國際社會應更多聲援香港民眾","createTime":"2019-07-22T14:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T14:21:13.000Z","uid":144372,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f0d026672375852cc58cf827468041e930e6dc","tid":1351002,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:20:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469399-20190720.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469399-20190720.htm&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=153b565a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469399-20190720.htm&h=d3ce557a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469399-20190720.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣的蔡英文總統，結束在加勒比海友邦的訪問，回程期間過境美國丹佛，停留兩晚。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文與美國參議院議員賈德納會面時談及香港，認為香港民眾追求民主自由的聲音，國際社會應給予更多的聲援與支持；美國與台灣共享價值，應該在香港議題上有更多的合作，表達對香港問題的關注。"},{"pid":"3066a409facfac02f1fa76a1d57a2153311baf24","tid":1351002,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:21:13.000Z","msg":"建制派及其政府 公然向香港市民發動恐怖襲擊！<br />\n<br />\n地鐵故意堅持開住車箱門，任由警黑合作虐打市民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港政府= 台灣鄭捷"}]}